de.hshannover.f4.trust.ifmapj.messages

Interface SubscribeRequest

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Request

    public interface SubscribeRequest
extends Request
    Interface to access data concerning a SubscribeRequest. MAPCs can subscribe to changes occurring on a MAPS. The underlying mechanism are subscriptions. A SubscribeRequest provides a MAPC the ability to create and delte subscriptions using SubscribeUpdate and SubscribeDelete elements, respectively.
    Author:
    aw
